The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, which are the main topics of the cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) category. The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) also suggests that the paper could be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves geometric distortion correction, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
